@NODE HISTORY "History"

        @{u}@{fg highlight}                       @{uu}

        History of POWER Recent
        @{u}                       @{fg text}@{uu}




    1.01 : -  Initial release (uses AMOS Pro).

    1.10 : -  Uses the new POWER Procedures 1.20
           -  Improved the loading of INDEX.
           -  Popup to front when the sorting is finished.
           -  Added Multi Wait during the loading
           -  Outputed text reformated

    2.00 : -  Completly rewritten in C language with MUI.
           -  Sorting feature removed.

    3.00 : -  Brand new interface
           -  Many more parameters
           -  Uses the TREE file in the prefs and in the RECENT file
           -  AmigaGuide and HTML format supported
           -  Splitting option available

    3.10 : -  Detailed some help bubble texts
           -  Stupid bug removed from `Update' TREE button. Should really
              update the listview now.
           -  In Text format, don't output anymore the directory header for
              empty dirs and don't output anymore empty files or extra menu
              file lines.
           -  In AmigaGuide format, don't create anymore links to empty or
              inexistant nodes.
           -  In HTML format, don't create anymore links to empty or inexistant
              nodes. Now, the menus to access subdirectories are contained only
              in a separate file.
           -  Removed some bugs causing crashes with HTML and Guide format.

@ENDNODE
